comments: Curry (GSW) is moving alongside Russell's (MIN) path and marginal contact occurs at the end of the drive.
Green (GSW) brings his hand towards Reid's (MIN) front and marginal contact occurs prior to the start of Reid's upward shooting motion.
Green (GSW) briefly grasps McDaniels' (MIN) arm and Green immediately releases McDaniels as he moves to contest Curry's (GSW) shot.
Russell (MIN) briefly grasps Poole's (GSW) arm and marginal contact occurs as they come around the pick.
As McDaniels (MIN) cuts across the perimeter, marginal contact occurs with Poole (GSW) as they come together following the dribble hand-off.
Poole (GSW) legally contests Russell's (MIN) jump shot, making "high-five" contact after the ball is released.
Russell (MIN) brings his hand towards Thompson's (GSW) front, and as he retracts his hand he deflects the ball away from Thompson.
Edwards (MIN) cleanly deflects the ball away from Looney (GSW) during rebounding.
Anderson (MIN) swipes his hand down and makes contact with Thompson's (GSW) arm as he is passing the ball.
Looney (GSW) makes contact with Anderson's (MIN) arm that causes him to lose control of the ball.
Anderson (MIN) clamps and holds Green's (GSW) arm, restricting his ability to bring both hands to the ball.
Green (GSW) is the last player to make contact with the ball before it goes out of bounds.
McDaniels (MIN) cuts across the perimeter and marginal contact occurs with Wiggins (GSW) as the defenders switch.
Thompson (GSW) is already in McDaniels' (MIN) path when contact occurs and he does not deliver contact.
Thompson (GSW) legally contests Russell's (MIN) jump shot attempt.
Green (GSW) contests Russell's (MIN) jump shot attempt and marginal contact occurs after the release.
Anderson (MIN) makes contact with Russell's (MIN) shot during its downward flight, but the ball does not have an opportunity to score.
Prince (MIN) is already in Wiggins' (GSW) path and is firming up when contact occurs.
Prince (MIN) legally contests Thompson's (GSW) jump shot attempt.
Poole (GSW) brings his hands towards Edwards' (MIN) body and marginal contact occurs as Edwards mistimes his jump for the rebound.
Edwards (MIN) is moving alongside Poole's (GSW) path and cleanly deflects the ball away from Poole.
Edwards (MIN) is the last player to touch the ball before the ball goes out of bounds.
Green (GSW) is the first to touch his pass to Curry (GSW).
Rivers (MIN) is already in Wiggins' (GSW) path when contact occurs and he does not deliver contact.
Wiggins (GSW) is moving alongside Edwards' (MIN) path and marginal contact occurs on the perimeter.
Green (GSW) absorbs the marginal contact as he contests Edwards' (MIN) driving shot attempt.
After communicating with the Replay Center, the ruling on the court (defensive goaltending) was confirmed.  Reid (MIN) makes contact with the ball after it makes contact with the backboard.
Rivers (MIN) is already in Wiggins' (GSW) path and does not deliver contact.
Wiggins (GSW) is already in Reid's (MIN) path and is firming up when contact occurs.
Wiggins (GSW) moves forward towards Edwards (MIN) and marginal contact occurs as Edwards moves forward towards the rim.
Green (GSW) and Reid (MIN) briefly engage and disengage as they pursue the rebound.
Curry (GSW) brings his arm towards Reid's (MIN) upper body and marginal contact occurs during the shot near the rim.
